      • isTextVisible

        boolean isTextVisible​(java.awt.Rectangle searchArea,
                      java.util.List<java.awt.Color> colors,
                      java.util.Map<java.lang.String,​int[][]> letterPatterns,
                      java.lang.String stringToFind)
        Reads the specific area, and returns true/false if it was able to read or not.
        Parameters:
        searchArea - A java.awt.Rectangle with the area you want to perform OCR on.
        colors - A java.util.List with java.awt.Colors in it that you'd like to use to read.
        letterPatterns - The map containing letter patterns for the OCR matching of the menu text.
        stringToFind - The string to search for in your given area.
        Returns:
        true/false if we found the text or not
